{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":24}],"page_start":1,"page_end":1,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"永远跟着毛主席走","authors":["赵桂兰〖HH/换行〗DW：山东济宁一中"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来到了日夜梦想的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受中央首长的检阅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同敬爱的领袖一起照相。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在绿茵茵的草地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百双眼睛向领袖们走来的路上探望；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那颗跳动的心啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象要蹦出胸膛一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光为什么突然明亮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，是毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席来到了我们的身旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪先别充满眼眶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我仔细看看毛主席："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席满面红光，魁伟健壮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他向我们挥手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我们指出了奋斗的方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着毛主席走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的决心比钢铁还坚强！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山东济宁一中 女民兵营营长 赵桂兰"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}